Subject: [PATCH 1/5] fix: Read from IndexedDB directly in uploadLocalToCloud

- Now reads directly from IndexedDB to avoid React stale closure issues
- Merges IndexedDB data with React state (prefers source with more data)
- Added detailed logging to diagnose data flow issues
- Increased timeout to 60 seconds per upload
- Removed old AcTracker Master Firebase directory
